Description:
You arrive at an elven house that is completely frozen.

Curiously, you have been able to open the door easily and inside, although frozen, everything seems to be somewhat tidy.

In the living room you find a couple of frozen elves, no doubt someone has moved them and placed them together. They are dead but at least the death was instantaneous, that comforts you a little.
DescriptionAction: There is little else you can do here but try to look for something of value...
